c_ohc=pUFYz6zdCIEQ7kNvgHiP5b-&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCJc9LceMDBJVOFeOd4wo9Gu-6xlCFtgAGtVXmsahwaGw&oe=66FA785D"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "cover.png", "id": "405044145251835", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/86796210_405044148585168_541174282990593081_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=EwJUXYUs964Q7kNvgEJnK71&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAv5cKZqmN7r3NDlMCWvkaOCvzrCd2C2NdkxsKHhdM1gw&oe=66FA900A"}, "display_name": "Bowliverse", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Bowliverse: The Ultimate VR Bowling Experience\n\nWelcome to \"Bowliverse,\" where the classic sport of bowling transcends the ordinary and enters a realm of immersive virtual reality. Prepare to embark on a cosmic adventure that transforms traditional bowling into an exhilarating and futuristic experience. Whether you're a seasoned bowler or new to the game, \"Bowliverse\" offers a fresh and captivating way to enjoy this beloved sport.\nGame Overview\n\n\"Bowliverse\" is a cutting-edge VR game that redefines the bowling experience by placing players in a vibrant cosmic arena. The game challenges your precision, skill, and timing as you aim to score points by knocking down pins in various celestial-themed lanes. Each game session offers a unique adventure, filled with stunning visuals and dynamic gameplay.", "short_description": "Bowliverse: The Ultimate VR Bowling Experience\n\nWelcome to \"Bowliverse,\" where the classic sport of bowling transcends the ordinary and enters a realm of immersive virtual reality. Prepare to embark on a cosmic adventure that transforms traditional bowling into an exhilarating and futuristic experience. Whether you're a seasoned bowler or new to the game, \"Bowliverse\" offers a fresh and captivating way to enjoy this beloved sport."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/bowliverse/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url